column2: SELECT input.*,  	po.ra AS sdss_ra, po.dec AS sdss_dec FROM MyDB.AKARImain_SDSSspecDR1#_bestobjid input 	INNER JOIN PhotoObjAll po ON po.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz pz ON pz.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN TwoMassXSC tmass ON tmass.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN FIRST            ON first.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid ORDER BY search_id
